warehouse

Interface IListener<TYPE>

  • Type Parameters:
    TYPE - the type of the listener. It denotes the type of the object that the notification is about.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IWarehouseListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ManagementServer, WarehouseManager

    public interface IListener<TYPE>
    This interface specifies the behavior of a listener. Listeners are notified about changes on objects. The type of the objects that trigger the notification are generic. This type can be further qualified in classes or interfaces that extend/implement this interface.
    Author:
    OOP

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void notifyChange(TYPE object)
      This method is called to inform the IListener about changes on the passed object.
